What my customer expects ??

Q - Qualifying Criteria
QQ - Order losing sensitive Criteria
OD / OW - Order Differentiators / Order Winners

( Exercise has to be done for each market ) 

Criteria                                                Weightage
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Right Type of Wood                                          QQ
Furniture must be blemish free                              OW (10%)
Durable Furniture                                           QQ
Attractive Designs                                          QQ
Time to Deliver (Lead Time) =< 10 days                      Q
Customer complaints to be address in =< 24 hrs              Q
Customer complaints to be closed in =< 5 days               Q
On-Time Delivery                                            QQ
On Time Complaints addressed                                QQ
On Time Complaints closed                                   QQ
Full Range of Products                                      Q
New designs every 6 months                                  OW(35%)
Range of designs in each product in the Range               OW(40%)
Customized Designs                                          OW(10%)  
Price                                                       OW(05%)
